## clarification

The report's statement that HEAD remained `4950c11baac4b70467be009e45dfead5d780cc6f` describes the commit against which the reported commands, source readings and mock harness executions were performed. The report was then added in commit `b870d97c6403cf3d434006567f22fc88086c3d68`, which became the remote branch tip before this addendum.

The original report is preserved without modification. This addendum does not promote, close, accept or remediate any observation. It records repository state only.

