## limitations

The Git blob identity was independently read from GitHub. The SHA-256 above is preserved from the producing session's handoff; this connector-only review did not independently stream the complete private blob into a local hashing process. The merge and subsequent remediation work must not treat that un-recomputed SHA-256 as stronger evidence than the Git blob and commit identities.
